    月    1     日\r\n                              書記官  葉乙成","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDV/111%2c%e5%8b%9e%e8%a8%b4%2c83%2c20221101%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDV,111,勞訴,83,20221101,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"勞訴","JNO":"83","JDATE":"20221101","JTITLE":"回復原職等"}